            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h3>Charlie Harper</h3>
                <p class="text-danger" style="font-size:20px"><em>"You know what the problem is? The women, the drinking... you look at me and think it's easy. What you don't see is the years of dedication that have made me the boozing ass wrangler I am today."</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters">
            <div class="col-lg-6 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h3>Hank Moody</h3>
                <p class="text-danger" style="font-size:20px"><em>"A morning of awkwardness is far better than a night of loneliness"</em></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('https://brokeassstuart.com/wp-content/pictsnShit/2017/01/file_162591_0_image_1.jpg');opacity:0.6"></div>
        </div><br /><br />
        <div class="row no-gutters">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('https://petiscos.jp/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Peter-x-Homer.jpg');opacity:0.6"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h2>Peter &amp; Homer</h2>
